item.title: About
item.description: About Austin Barnes and Cinderblock.tech Welcome to Cinderblock.tech! My name is Austin Barnes, and this website is my personal side project where I share a variety of content. I’m a tech enthusiast with a passion for exploring different aspects of technology. In my professional life, I work as an Infrastructure Engineer at Battelle. Prior to that, I gained experience as a Linux Support for Pennsylvania College of Technology and as a Network Technician for Jersey Shore Area School District.
